WWW-Yandex-Catalog-LookupSite

This module retrieves a website's Thematic Index of Citing, checks 
website's presence in Yandex Catalog, retrieves it's descriptions 
as recorded in the catalog, and the list of categories it belongs to.

This module uses LWP::Simple for making requests to Yandex Catalog.

Please see documentation for usage.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc WWW::Yandex::Catalog::LookupSite

